<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>115</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kilima kando ya mji
 Alikufa Bwana;
 Kuokoa wakosaji
 Akateswa sana.

[V2]
 Kabisa hayasemeki,
 Mateso dhaifu
 Alikufa mwenye Haki
 Tupate wokovu.

[V3]
 Alimwaga damu yake
 Ili tuwe wema,
 Tufae kukaa kwake
 Mbinguni daima.

[V4]
 Hatuna mwenye imani
 Aliye na haki,
 Wa kutosha yetu deni,
 Rafiki Yesu tu.

[V5]
 Alijua peke yake
 Kufungu Mbingu
 Ufunguo damu yake
 Kondoo wa Mungu.

[V6]
 Aliyetupenda hivyo
 Nasi tumpende,
 Tukamtumai vivyo
 Na kazi tutende.</lyrics>
<title>Kilima Kando Ya Mji TZR115</title>
</song>